title: Kristin Shares A Very Important Life Lesson That Resonated With Her
description:
At first, Kristin didn't want to admit it, but she found wisdom from an unexpected source. Who? Kendall Jenner. She said something that resonated with her that had everything to do with protecting your inner child.
